Bini Smaghi Says ECB Has No Intention to Transfer Balance Sheet

-- B y   R a i n e r   B u e r g i n   a n d   M e e r a   L o u i s
-- 
2011-09-25T13:55:56Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-25/bini-smaghi-says-ecb-has-no-intention-to-transfer-balance-sheet.html
European Central Bank Executive
Board member Lorenzo Bini Smaghi said the central bank has “no
intention to transfer our balance sheet to anybody else.”  He was speaking at a panel discussion in  Washington  today
at which the role of the European Financial Stability Facility
was also discussed.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rainer Buergin at 
 rbuergin1@bloomberg.net  